description.plain:
Valentin Brunel, better known as Kungs is a 25 year old french producer and DJ, born in Toulon, France.
He became popular by posting on Soundcloud some remixes. As his popularity grew up he was chosen by David Guetta to perform his Opening act.
The released of his remix of the Cookin' On 3 Burners' title, “This Girl” in February 2016 allowed him to reach worlwide fame.
After spending his summer 2016 touring across the world. He released his debut album on 4 November 2016
